HEADWORD: Pinching
<hw>Pinch"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Compressing; nipping; griping;
niggardly; <as>as, <ex>pinching</ex> cold; a <ex>pinching</ex>
parsimony.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Pinching bar</b></col>, <cd>a pinch bar. See
